#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.squeeze.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.squeeze"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:1 of
msgid "Remove single-dimensional entries from the shape of a tensor."
msgstr "从张量的形状中移除单维度条目。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:3 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:5 of
msgid ""
"Selects a subset of the single-dimensional entries in the shape. If an "
"axis is selected with shape entry greater than one, an error is raised."
msgstr "选择形状中的部分单维度条目。如果所选轴的形状条目大于一，则会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:10 of
msgid ""
"**squeezed** -- The input tensor, but with all or a subset of the "
"dimensions of length 1 removed. This is always `a` itself or a view into "
"`a`."
msgstr ""
"**squeezed** -- 输入张量，但所有或部分长度为1的维度已被移除。这始终是 `a`"
" 本身或 `a` 的视图。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:15 of
msgid "If `axis` is not `None`, and an axis being squeezed is not of length 1"
msgstr "如果 `axis` 不为 `None`，且被压缩的轴长度不为1"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`expand_dims`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:20 of
msgid "The inverse operation, adding singleton dimensions"
msgstr "逆操作，添加单例维度"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`reshape`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:23 of
msgid "Insert, remove, and combine dimensions, and resize existing ones"
msgstr "插入、移除和合并维度，以及调整现有维度的大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.squeeze.squeeze:26 of
